extends baseEmail

block content
  p Dear #{fullName},
  p We are thrilled to inform you that your account with [Your Company/Platform Name] has been successfully approved by our administrators!
  p You now have full access to our platform, and we’re excited to have you as part of our community.
  p You can log in and start exploring the features available to you right away.
  hr
  p Account Details:
  ul
    li Full Name: #{fullName}
    li Email: #{email}
    li Role: #{role}
    li Status: Approved ✅
  hr
  p If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
  p We appreciate your patience and look forward to having you as a valued member of our platform!
  p Best Regards,
  p Stealth
